 select multiple contiguous cols/rows: 
    Select column specific column, and use SHIFT+ right arrow to reach the desire column
    Ex
      want to select column A to column E. Do this by
      Select column A then push SHIFT+ right arrow to reach column E
 

select multiple non-contiguous cols/rows: 
   Select specific column , then hold CTRL and select another desire column 
   Ex
      want to select column A and column E. Do this by
      Select column A then hold CTRL and select column E 
     
